snippet.title: Panchayat Season 3 - Official Trailer | Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav | May 28
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 3 Official Trailer
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa
Produced by Arunabh Kumar
Directed by Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by Chandan Kumar
Production Company - The Viral Fever 

Official Release Date May 28, 2024 on Prime Video India.

About:
As the Panchayat elections approach, both Pradhan and Bhushan gangs engage in a fierce battle to uplift their public image. Navigating the murky waters of Phulera politics, Abhishek does his best to maintain his objectivity.

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

#PanchayatOnPrime #Panchayat

snippet.title: Double ISMART Teaser ( Telugu) | Ram Pothineni | Sanjay Dutt | Puri Jagannadh | Charmme Kaur |
snippet.description:
Watch the #DoubleISMARTTeaser Telugu here!!

#DoubleISMART is an Indian Action Entertainer film, written and directed by Puri Jagannnadh featuring Ram Pothineni in the lead role will be seen in a Massier character than iSmart Shankar. Also stars Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar in the prominent roles. Produced by Puri Jagannadh and Charmme Kaur under Puri Connects, The film will have a much bigger span and will be made with a high budget on a large scale with top-class technical standards. Double iSmart will be releasing in Telugu, Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam, and Hindi languages.

Cast: Ram Pothineni, Sanjay Dutt, Kavya Thapar, Bani J, Ali, Getup Sreenu, Sayaji Shinde, Makrand Deshpande,  Temper Vamsi & others.

snippet.description:
Presenting the timeless love song ‘Dekhha Tenu’ from the film ‘Mr. and Mrs. Mahi’ - out now! Starring the lead cast – Janhvi Kapoor and Rajkummar Rao in the video, the video depicts their love story in the movie. With the original song ‘Say Shava Shava’ composed by Aadesh Shrivastava and penned by Sameer Anjaan, the new version is composed and written by Jaani. Sung in the captivating voice of Mohammad Faiz, this song is a magnificent treat to the ears.

snippet.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: Official World Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
Available November 15, 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Watch the official cinematic world premiere trailer of Assassin's Creed Shadows.
An Audio Described version is also available in English in the settings of the video.

Learn more: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows

Full gameplay reveal in June 2024.

About Assassin's Creed Shadows:

In Assassin’s Creed Shadows, you will live the intertwined stories of Naoe, an adept shinobi Assassin from Iga Province, and Yasuke, the powerful African samurai of historical legend. Against the backdrop of the turbulent late Sengoku period, this remarkable duo will discover their common destiny as they usher in a new era for Japan. 

From chaos to purpose, from darkness to light. A new Creed rises over Japan.

th.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: ตัวอย่างภาพยนตร์รอบปฐมทัศน์อย่างเป็นทางการพร้อมกันทั่วโลก
th.description:
วางจำหน่ายในวันที่ 15 พฤศจิกายน 2567: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

รับชมตัวอย่างภาพยนตร์รอบปฐมทัศน์อย่างเป็นทางการพร้อมกันทั่วโลกของ Assassin's Creed Shadows
มีเวอร์ชันบรรยายเสียงเป็นภาษาอังกฤษในการตั้งค่าของวิดีโอ

ดูรายละเอียดเพิ่มเติม: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
ดูเพิ่มเติม: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

เกมเพลย์เต็มรูปแบบจะถูกเปิดเผยในเดือนมิถุนายน 2567 นี้

เกี่ยวกับ Assassin's Creed Shadows:

ใน Assassin’s Creed Shadows คุณจะได้สัมผัสเรื่องราวของสองมือสังหารที่มาบรรจบกันระหว่าง Naoe นักฆ่าชิโนบิฝีมือดีจากจังหวัดอิงะ และ Yasuke ซามูไรในตำนานชาวแอฟริกันผู้แข็งแกร่งที่ถูกจารึกไว้ในประวัติศาสตร์ ท่ามกลางความวุ่นวายในช่วงปลายยุคเซ็นโงกุ สุดยอดมือสังหารทั้งสองจะต้องเผชิญชะตากรรมร่วมกัน ในขณะที่พวกเขาก้าวไปสู่ยุคใหม่ของแดนอาทิตย์อุทัย

จากความมืดมิดสู่แสงสว่างแห่งชีวิต จากความวุ่นวายสู่จุดมุ่งหมายที่ชัดเจน ภาคีกลุ่มใหม่ได้แผ่ขยายไปทั่วแคว้นแดนอาทิตย์อุทัย

pl.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: pierwszy zwiastun, światowa premiera
pl.description:
Premiera gry 15 listopada 2024 r.: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Obejrzyj oficjalny zwiastun filmowy z okazji światowej premiery Assassin's Creed Shadows.
W ustawieniach wideo dostępna jest także wersja z audiodeskrypcją w języku angielskim.

Dowiedz się więcej: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Obejrzyj więcej: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Pełna prezentacja rozgrywki w czerwcu 2024 r.

O Assassin's Creed Shadows:

W Assassin's Creed Shadows poznasz splatające się losy Naoe, asasynki shinobi z prowincji Iga, oraz Yasuke, potężnego afrykańskiego samuraja z legend. W czasach burzliwego okresu późnego Sengoku ten nadzwyczajny duet odkryje swe wspólne przeznaczenie, zapoczątkowując nową erę w historii Japonii.

Z chaosu ku sensowi, z ciemności ku światłu. W Japonii pojawia się nowe kredo.

it.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: anteprima mondiale del trailer di presentazione ufficiale
it.description:
Disponibile dal 15 novembre 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Guarda il trailer di presentazione ufficiale di Assassin's Creed Shadows in anteprima mondiale.
Una versione con audiodescrizione in lingua inglese è inoltre disponibile tra le impostazioni del video.

Scopri di più: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Guarda altro: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Presentazione completa del gioco in arrivo a giugno 2024.

Informazioni su Assassin's Creed Shadows:

In Assassin's Creed Shadows, vivrai le storie intrecciate di Naoe, un'abile Assassina shinobi della provincia di Iga, e di Yasuke, il leggendario e possente samurai africano realmente esistito Sullo sfondo del movimentato tardo periodo Sengoku, questi due guerrieri formidabili scopriranno di avere un destino in comune e contribuiranno a inaugurare una nuova era del Giappone. 

Dal caos alla convinzione, dall'oscurità alla luce. Un nuovo Credo sorge in Giappone.

tr.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: Resmî Dünya Prömiyeri Fragmanı
tr.description:
15 Kasım 2024'te çıkıyor: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Assassin's Creed Shadows resmî sinematik dünya prömiyeri fragmanını izleyin.
Video ayarlarında mevcut olan İngilizce Sesli Betimleme seçeneğiyle de izlenebilir.

Ayrıntılı bilgi: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Daha fazla içerik izleyin: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Tam oynanış gösterimi Haziran 2024'te geliyor.

Assassin's Creed Shadows hakkında:

Assassin’s Creed Shadows'ta Iga vilayetinden usta Şinobi Suikastçı Naoe ile kudretiyle efsaneleşmiş Afrika kökenli samuray Yasuke'nin kesişen hikâyelerine yakından tanıklık edeceksiniz. Çalkantılı geç Sengoku döneminin gölgesinde mücadele eden bu iki iddialı savaşçı, Japonya için yeni bir devrin kapılarını aralarken ortak kaderlerini de birlikte keşfedecek. 

Kaostan istikrara, karanlıktan aydınlığa... Yeni Creed güneşi Japonya'da yükseliyor.

fr.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows – Trailer cinématique en première mondiale
fr.description:
Disponible le 15 novembre 2024 : https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Regardez la bande-annonce cinématique officielle en première mondiale d'Assassin's Creed Shadows.
Une version en audiodescription est disponible en anglais depuis les paramètres de la vidéo.

En savoir plus : https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Pour en voir plus : https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Présentation complète du gameplay en juin 2024.

À propos d'Assassin's Creed Shadows :

Dans Assassin's Creed Shadows, vous découvrirez les destins croisés de Naoe, une Assassin shinobi de la province d'Iga, et Yasuke, le puissant et légendaire samouraï d'origine africaine. Dans le contexte mouvementé de la fin de l'époque Sengoku, ces deux alliés inattendus découvriront le destin qui les unit alors que le Japon entre dans une nouvelle ère. 

Du chaos à la détermination, de l'obscurité à la lumière. Un nouveau Crédo se lève sur le Japon.

pt-BR.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: Trailer Cinemático Oficial da Estreia Mundial
pt-BR.description:
Disponível em 15 de novembro de 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Assista ao trailer cinemático oficial da estreia mundial de Assassin's Creed Shadows.
Uma versão com audiodescrição em inglês está disponível nas configurações do vídeo.

Saiba mais em https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Assista mais: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Revelação de jogabilidade completa em junho de 2024.

Sobre Assassin's Creed Shadows:

Em Assassin's Creed Shadows, você vivenciará as histórias interligadas de Naoe, uma assassina shinobi extremamente hábil da província de Iga, e de Yasuke, poderoso samurai africano de importância histórica. Nos anos finais do turbulento período Sengoku, essa dupla extraordinária descobrirá seu destino em comum conforme dá início a uma nova era no Japão. 

Do caos ao propósito, da escuridão à luz. Um novo Credo surge no Japão.

ar.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: عرض الكشف السينمائي العالمي الرسمي
ar.description:
تتوفر في 15 نوفمبر 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

شاهدوا عرض الكشف السينمائي العالمي الرسمي لـAssassin's Creed Shadows.
النسخة الموصوفة صوتيًا متاحة أيضاً باللغة الإنجليزية في إعدادات الفيديو.

للمزيد من التفاصيل: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
لمشاهدة المزيد: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

الكشف الكامل لأسلوب اللعب في يونيو 2024.

عن Assassin's Creed Shadows:

في Assassin’s Creed Shadows، ستعيشون قصص نآوي المعقدة، وهي أساسن شينوبي ماهرة من مقاطعة إيغا، وياسوكي الساموراي الأفريقي القوي من الأسطورة التاريخية. على خلفية أواخر فترة سينغوكو المضطربة، سيكتشف هذا الثنائي الرائع مصيره المشترك بينما يدخلان حقبة جديدة في اليابان.

من الفوضى إلى الغاية، ومن الظلام إلى النور. قصة Creed جديدة تطل على اليابان.

de.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: Offizieller Weltpremieren-Trailer
de.description:
Verfügbar ab 15. November 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Sieh dir den offiziellen Weltpremieren-Trailer von Assassin's Creed Shadows an.
Eine Version mit englischer Audiobeschreibung ist in den Videoeinstellungen verfügbar.

Mehr erfahren: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
Mehr sehen: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Umfassende Gameplay-Enthüllung im Juni 2024.

Über Assassin's Creed Shadows:

In Assassin's Creed Shadows durchlebst du die miteinander verflochtenen Geschichten von Naoe, einer geübten Shinobi-Assassinin aus der Provinz Iga, und Yasuke, dem mächtigen afrikanischen Samurai aus historischen Legenden. Vor der Kulisse der turbulenten späten Sengoku-Periode entdeckt dieses bemerkenswerte Duo sein gemeinsames Schicksal, während es ein neues Zeitalter in Japan einläutet. 

Aus Verwirrung wird Bestimmung, aus Dunkelheit Licht. Ein neues Kredo erhebt sich in Japan.

zh-Hans.title: 《刺客信条：影》 - 官方全球首秀宣传片
zh-Hans.description:
2024 年 11 月 15 日发布：https://ubi.li/rEDXA

观看《刺客信条：影》官方全球首秀宣传片。
在视频设置中可选择英文版的音频描述。

了解更多：https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
观看更多：https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

实机演示将于 2024 年 6 月面世。

关于《刺客信条：影》：

在《刺客信条：影》中，你将体验两位主角紧密交织的故事：来自伊贺国的忍者刺客高手奈绪江，以及强大的传奇非洲武士弥助。在日本战国末期动荡不安的背景下，这对非凡的主角将逐渐揭开他们共同命运的神秘面纱，带领日本走入全新的时代。

在混乱中找到前进的目标，褪去往日的黑暗，迎向明媚的未来。新的信条在日本立下。

ko.title: 어쌔신 크리드 섀도우스: 공식 시네마틱 월드 프리미어 트레일러
ko.description:
2024년 11월 15일 출시: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

‘어쌔신 크리드 섀도우스’의 공식 시네마틱 월드 프리미어 트레일러를 감상하세요.
동영상 설정을 통해 오디오 설명 버전을 영어로 이용할 수 있습니다.

더 알아보기: https://www.assassincreed.com/shadows
더 보기: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

전체 게임플레이는 2024년 6월에 공개됩니다.

'어쌔신 크리드 섀도우스 정보:

‘어쌔신 크리드 섀도우스’에서 여러분은 이가 지방의 뛰어난 시노비 암살자인 나오에와 실제 역사에도 등장하는 강력한 아프리카 출신 사무라이인 야스케 사이에 뒤얽힌 서사를 접하게 됩니다. 격동의 센고쿠 시대 후기 속에서 이 비범한 두 인물은 일본의 새로운 시대를 이끌어가며 공동의 운명을 발견하게 됩니다.

혼돈에서 목적을 찾고, 어둠 속에서 빛을 찾아라. 일본에서 새로운 신조가 비상합니다.

es.title: Assassin's Creed Shadows: Estreno mundial del tráiler cinemático oficial
es.description:
Disponible el 15 de noviembre de 2024: https://ubi.li/rEDXA

Una versión audiodescrita en inglés también estará disponible en los ajustes del vídeo.

Ver más: https://youtu.be/Nszrx939ZVA

Presentación completa del gameplay en junio de 2024.

Sobre Assassin's Creed Shadows:

Sumérgete en Assassin's Creed Shadows y vive las historias entrelazadas de Naoe, una experta Assassin shinobi de la provincia de Iga, y Yasuke, el poderoso samurai africano de las leyendas históricas. Con los últimos años del turbulento periodo Sengoku como telón de fondo, este dúo peculiar descubrirá su destino común en los comienzos de una nueva era para Japón.

Del caos, a la razón; de la oscuridad, a la luz. Un nuevo Credo surge en Japón.

ja.title: 『アサシン クリード シャドウズ』公式シネマティック ワールドプレミア トレーラー
ja.description:
2024年11月15日発売予定：https://ubi.li/rEDXA

『アサシン クリード シンジケート』について：
『アサシン クリード シャドウズ』でプレイヤーは、伊賀者にして優れた忍のアサシンである奈緒江、そして歴史に語り継がれている屈強なアフリカ人の侍である弥助、その互いに交差する物語を体験する戦国時代末期、生き馬の目を抜くような激動の乱世において、類まれなる二人は互いに相通ずる使命を見出し、新たな時代を目前にした大いなる戦いの行方に深く関わっていく。
混沌から秩序へ、闇影から光明へ日ノ本に新たな信条が生まれる

Shiddat Episode 30 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 14th May 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS! HAALAND BRACE FIRES CITY TO WITHIN TOUCHING DISTANCE OF TITLE | Tottenham 0-2 Man City
snippet.description:
Erling Haaland’s second half brace saw City secure a priceless 2-0 victory at Spurs – and moved Pep Guardiola’s side back to the top of the Premier League table and within one win of an historic fourth straight title.

It marked City’s first-ever league victory – and goals – at the Tottenham Hotspur Stadium with both arriving on the most auspicious of occasions.

It was a tense, eventful night with City also having to bring substitute ‘keeper Stefan Ortega Moreno on for Ederson midway through the second half after the Brazilian hurt his head in a collision with Cristian Romero.

And the German made his impact immediately felt with a series of quite outstanding saves - including one stunning block to deny Son Heung-Min - to keep the hosts out.

snippet.title: CDs ARE BACK! 16 LAKH GB Storage in just 1 CD - New Breakthrough Technology
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo Sign App absolutely free - https://www.odoo.com/r/zxN

CDs are making a comeback. Believe it or not, there is a new technology through which you can now pack 1.6 petabytes of data into one CD! Once considered obsolete, CDs are making a triumphant comeback, defying expectations. Recently, researchers in China have developed this revolutionary CD technology, enabling a single CD to hold a staggering 1.6 petabytes or simply 16 lakh gigabytes of data (Pg. no. 2). To put it into perspective, to store such colossal amounts of data, companies like Google typically require a server room the size of a small warehouse. But the question is will this technology could be succesful? What will be the price of it and ofcourse will it be available to the masses? Let's find out!!

snippet.description:
Brand Partner:

Call 8891062666 or register for a call back here: https://forms.gle/Zw9hy1GVYieCqai4A

PwC Certified Tax Professional Modules ഉൾപ്പെടുന്ന Business Accounting കോഴ്‌സിലൂടെ Theory പഠനത്തോടൊപ്പം തന്നെ മോക്ക് വെബ്സൈറ്റുകൾ വഴി പ്രാക്ടീസ് ചെയ്ത് തയ്യാറെടുക്കാം. അതുപോലെ, 4.25 ലക്ഷത്തിലേറെ കമ്പനികൾ ഉപയോഗിക്കുന്ന SAP യുടെ പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട മൊഡ്യൂളുകളായ SAP MM, SAP FICO-യും പഠിക്കാം. snippet.title: Wicked - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Everyone deserves the chance to fly. Watch the #WickedMovie trailer now.  🧹🫧

Apply to Shiz University at https://www.shizuniversity.com

Pre-save ‘Wicked The Soundtrack’ at https://wickedthesoundtrack.com
-----
Subscribe to the Wicked YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/wickedmovie
TikTok:  https://www.tiktok.com/@wickedmovie
Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/wickedmovie
X: https://twitter.com/wickedmovie
Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/wickedmovie/
Official Site:  https://www.wickedmovie.com/

After two decades as one of the most beloved and enduring musicals on the stage, Wicked makes its long-awaited journey to the big screen as a spectacular, generation-defining cinematic event this holiday season. 

Wicked, the untold story of the witches of Oz, stars Emmy, Grammy and Tony winning powerhouse Cynthia Erivo (Harriet, Broadway’s The Color Purple) as Elphaba, a young woman, misunderstood because of her unusual green skin, who has yet to discover her true power, and Grammy-winning, multi-platinum recording artist and global superstar Ariana Grande as Glinda, a popular young woman, gilded by privilege and ambition, who has yet to discover her true heart. 
 
The two meet as students at Shiz University in the fantastical Land of Oz and forge an unlikely but profound friendship. Following an encounter with The Wonderful Wizard of Oz, their friendship reaches a crossroads and their lives take very different paths. Glinda's unflinching desire for popularity sees her seduced by power, while Elphaba's determination to remain true to herself, and to those around her, will have unexpected and shocking consequences on her future. Their extraordinary adventures in Oz will ultimately see them fulfill their destinies as Glinda the Good and the Wicked Witch of the West. 
 
The film also stars Oscar® winner Michelle Yeoh as Shiz University’s regal headmistress Madame Morrible; Jonathan Bailey (Bridgerton, Fellow Travelers) as Fiyero, a roguish and carefree prince; Tony nominee Ethan Slater (Broadway’s Spongebob Squarepants, Fosse/Verdon) as Boq, an altruistic Munchkin student; Marissa Bode in her feature-film debut as Nessarose, Elphaba’s favored sister; and pop culture icon Jeff Goldblum as the legendary Wizard of Oz.
 
The cast of characters includes Pfannee and ShenShen, two conniving compatriots of Glinda played by Emmy nominee Bowen Yang (Saturday Night Live) and Bronwyn James (Harlots), and a new character created for the film, Miss Coddle, played by Tony nominee Keala Settle (The Greatest Showman). 
 
Directed by acclaimed filmmaker Jon M. Chu (Crazy Rich Asians, In the Heights), Wicked is the first chapter of a two-part immersive, cultural celebration. Wicked Part Two is scheduled to arrive in theaters on November 26, 2025.
 
Wicked is produced by Marc Platt (La La Land, The Little Mermaid), whose films, television shows and stage productions have earned a combined 46 Oscar® nominations, 58 Emmy nominations and 36 Tony nominations, and by multiple Tony winner David Stone (Kimberly Akimbo, Next to Normal), with whom Platt produced the blockbuster Wicked stage musical. The executive producers are David Nicksay, Stephen Schwartz and Jared LeBoff. 
 
Based on the bestselling novel by Gregory Maguire, Wicked is adapted for the screen by the stage production’s book writer Winnie Holzman and by legendary Grammy and Oscar® winning composer and lyricist Stephen Schwartz. The Broadway stage musical is produced by Universal Stage Productions, Marc Platt, the Araca Group, Jon B. Platt and David Stone.

snippet.title: "Exclusive: YS Jagan Mohan Reddy & Family Cast Votes in Bhakarapuram | Election Day Coverage"
snippet.description:
Description: Join Sakshi TV for exclusive coverage of the crucial election day as Chief Minister YS Jagan Mohan Reddy, along with his family members including wife YS Bharathi Reddy and daughters Harsha and Varsha, exercises their democratic right at Bhakarapuram school premises. Witness the moment as they cast both their votes, one for the Assembly and another for the Parliament constituency. Stay tuned to Sakshi TV for minute-to-minute updates and comprehensive analysis of the election proceedings.

వైఎస్సార్‌ కడప జిల్లా భాకరాపురం పోలింగ్‌బూత్‌లో ముఖ్యమంత్రి వైఎస్‌ జగన్‌మోహన్‌ రెడ్డి, ఆయన కుటుంబం ఓటు హక్కు వినియోగించుకుంది. ముఖ్యమంత్రి భార్య వైఎస్‌ భారతీ రెడ్డి, ఆయన కుమార్తెలు హర్ష మరియు వర్ష.. ఉదయం భాకరాపురం పాఠశాలలో ఏర్పాటు చేసిన పోలింగ్‌ బూత్‌కు వెళ్లి తమ ఓటు హక్కు (పార్లమెంటు మరియు అసెంబ్లీ) వినియోగించుకున్నారు. 

ఆంధ్రప్రదేశ్‌ ఎన్నికలకు సంబంధించిన అన్ని అప్‌డేట్స్‌ను సాక్షి టీవీ ఎప్పటికప్పుడు ఎక్స్‌క్లూజివ్‌గా మీ ముందుంచుతుంది.

snippet.description:

Episode 4084: Bina Mewa Kare Sabki Seva
--------------------------------------------------------
Kurmura Kumar schemes to take credit for the Tapu Sena's good deeds and profit from work he didn't do. Jethalal faces challenges due to Chana Kumar. Eventually, others are inspired by the Tapu Sena's positive impact and join in their efforts.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 4084, 14 May 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Love, Sex, Dhokha ft @aarushbhola17 @Lailavlogss | Sadhika Sehgal | Aarush Bhola & Laila Podcast
snippet.description:
Today we are in conversation with the iconic duo known for their friendship, West Delhi swag, and raw, easy-going charm - Aarush Bhola and Laila (Varun Yadav). Hop on this rollercoaster of fun where our host Sadhika Sehgal asks the most burning questions: Why do they look so alike? Who receives more compliments from the ladies? Their "game" with women, and of course, the big one - Are they single? We also explore their take on "Situationships", romance and marriage plans.

Aarush Bhola shares his breakup story and what he did to overcome his heartbreak in this interview.. The discussion takes a turn as they share how they support each other through breakups while still maintaining their signature banter. The conversation dives into the heart of their friendships, their individual personalities, and Varun's aka Laila’s decision to leave his office job, spiced up with Delhi slangs and crazy stories from their boy nights.

They compare their individual dating experiences, discussing red and green flags in relationships and what they look for in their future partners. No topic is off-limits, including their run-ins with the police during their trip to Bali. In this Aarush Bhola and Laila podcast, they also fondly share their experiences of their recent trip to Goa and Thailand. They talk about the kind of fights they get into and how all of it just signifies how the boys care for each other and what male friendships are all about.

Talking about their obsession with fitness, Aarush shares his take on gyming and transformation. Both of them reveal why gym gives them a "main character energy" while debunking myths surrounding it. They tackle tough topics with fun like cheating and conflicts within their group, shedding light on the complexities of male friendships.

From their views on the "No Fap" concept to their fantasies and strategies for turning on women, this podcast with Aarush Bhola and Laila is filled with real, unfiltered banter that is very relatable to young Indian males. You won't want to miss this wild ride through the lives of Aarush Bhola and Laila, where you can find everything about them from their regrets to fantasies!

Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats.

Get ready for a cinematic treat of the coming together of the JATT & JAATNI (Ammy Virk & Sonam Bajwa), with the official teaser of 'KUDI HARYANE VAL DI' / ‘CHORI HARYANE AALI’ releasing worldwide in cinemas on 14th June 2024!!

Presented by Ramara Films, written and directed by Rakesh Dhawan (Writer of Honsla Rakh & Chal Mera Putt, Director of Aaja Mexico Chaliye), produced by Pawan Gill, Aman Gill, Sunny Gill (Producers of Shadaa & Puaada)

This is a fun comedy, cross-cultural Punjabi-Haryanvi romance entertainer, about a loveable Punjabi Jatt (Ammy Virk) who crosses paths with the lively Haryanvi Jaatni (Sonam Bajwa). It’s love at first sight for this desi Jatt, who once didn’t care for anything associated with his family legacy of wrestling but will now go to any lengths to prove his love for the game to impress his lady love, but will this be enough?

snippet.title: हंसते हुए Iyer ने मारा Abdul को धक्का | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah| Gokuldham Ki Hasya Kathayen
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Jethalal is going on a trip and asks Bagha to book tickets. Jethalal tries to convince Taarak to join him for the trip. He is also happy as Babita will come along. But, are the tickets confirmed?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 790
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from "Gokuldham Ki Hasya Kathayen' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQHqAgGNhC8DFeU5UFpnwSr

Shiddat Episode 29 [Eng Sub] - Muneeb Butt - Anmol Baloch - Digitally Presented by PEL - 13th May 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Shiddat Digitally Presented by PEL

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.title: A Glimpse of My Postpartum Day | Post-Natal Treatment
snippet.description:
Life get a reschedule after being a new mom with a new born. The priority changes, time is spent more with the baby. Rest everything can wait or has to wait because your baby needs you 24/7. 

Am forutnate enough to have my parents here with me for a help and its such a relief when i had my mom beside me during my labor. My pregnancy and delivery has a lot more to tell this time and i shall share on that in another video. 

Hope you all are doing great and i missed you all. But i will have to take my time to make more vlogs because right now am spending my maximum time with my lil one.

Take care

Love you All !!!
•••••

snippet.description:

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

snippet.title: K For Kalyanam - Video Song | Guruvayoorambala Nadayil | Prithviraj | Basil | Anaswara | Ankit Menon
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Malayalam

Presenting the second single "K For Kalyanam" from 'Guruvayoor Ambalanadayil' starring Prithviraj Sukumaran, Basil Joseph, Nikhila Vimal and others. Directed by Vipin Das. Music Composed by Ankit Menon.

Song Credits:-
K For Kalyanam
Music Composed, Arranged & Produced by Ankit Menon

Vocals by Ankit Menon, Milan Joy, Himna Hilary, Aruna Mary George, Indu Deepu, Sharath, Neelima P Aryan, Parvatish Pradeep 
Lyrics: Suhail Koya

Female Chorus: Sony Mohan, Avani Malhar, Gayathri Rajiv
Music production: Parvatish Pradeep, Abin Thomas, Electronic Kili, Arcado 
Mix and master: Balu Thankachan (20db Studios)

Guitars: Ashwin Aryan 
Mandolin and Charango: Amar Sangam
Shehnai: Gopi
Music Assistant: Sachin Sivadas 
Recorded by: Tamzid Rahman, Amal Mithu, Amalraj 
Studios: Space Cat Studio (Mumbai), M Lounge (Kochi), Audiogene Studios (Kochi)
Music coordinators: KD Vincent, R Babu (Chennai)

Movie Credits:-
Director: Vipin Das 
Producers: Supriya Menon, Mukesh R Mehta, C V Sarathi
Banner: Prithviraj Productions Pvt Ltd and E4 Entertainment 
Writer: Deepu Pradeep
DOP: Neeraj Revi
Editor: John Kutty
Music: Ankit Menon
Choreography: Shobi Paulraj
Executive Producer: Harris Desom

Costume: Aswathy Jayakumar
Make Up: Sudhi Surendran

Stills: Jestin James Rohith K Suresh
Teaser Cut: Don Max
VFX: DTM VFX 
Opening Titles: Sarath Vinu
Subtitles: Vivek Ranjith
Title Design: Sarcasanam
DI: Color Planet Studios
Online Marketing: Poffactio / 10G Media 
Marketing: Catalyst 
Music Partner: Saregama South 

Lyrics:-
Heart beat heart beat 
what I tell you what a waste
Konjam koode slowly pokamo 

Glass chillin kanavalle 
Drop cheythal udayile 
Nenje neeyum slowly pokamo 

Meath motham padarana pani pole pakarum disease premam appa cholile 
Kakka kothum karalinte nadukk njan pedakumbho paattu vekkan DJ chollille 

A ninne karachillokke pinne manasilente pookutty padakanghalmaranenne 

K4 kalynam what a beautiful day 

Thekkennnaro vannittunde 
Kanda chodyam 
Pinnenthunde ? 

porayaake moodunnunde melam 

Aayiramaashakal aanayitte 
Nira kathirumotte thottu shapadhamitte

Nenjumme kanavukalorukki veche 
Palathadukki veche 
Chilathothikki veche

Niramellaam cherunne 
Palathonnaayi theerunne 
Kulirange kerunne

Ithu kalyana raav 

Oru paattu mooliyathu ketta paade pala naavilu cheranithu 
Pala poovu kondu cheru  thoranamayathu theeranapolayithu 

vari variyaayi vilambi varu 
Thuru thure ni 
Madhuramidu 
Thavilukalil 
Veralu kodu 

Kaathukal kaathirunnaa
Swarme 

Mozhi thaen karimbe 
Mizhi neer munabe 
Mukhamaake - yoraambujamaayi virinje  

Edi vanne orungaloke pinne 
Kanakk kooti kaathirikanaval ceremonye 
K for kalayanam what a beautiful day
